00:00:06.325 --> 00:00:11.537
(Months earlier. The day
of Shen Changning's grand wedding)

00:00:14.562 --> 00:00:17.537
(Shen Changning and Xi Yan
meet for the first time)

00:00:52.320 --> 00:00:53.039
Young Lady.

00:00:53.159 --> 00:00:54.290
Please, do not look anymore.

00:00:54.320 --> 00:00:55.920
Today is your big day of joy,

00:00:56.399 --> 00:00:58.039
yet we encounter a funeral procession.

00:00:58.240 --> 00:00:59.320
It is far too inauspicious.

00:00:59.590 --> 00:01:00.880
The deceased hold high respect.

00:01:01.439 --> 00:01:02.359
Let us give way.

00:01:14.280 --> 00:01:15.359
Help me.

00:01:16.719 --> 00:01:17.840
Let me out.

00:01:18.760 --> 00:01:19.480
Stop.

00:01:20.130 --> 00:01:21.760
There are clearly sounds
coming from inside.

00:01:21.760 --> 00:01:22.760
Let me out.

00:01:22.879 --> 00:01:24.359
Why do you turn a deaf ear?

00:01:25.040 --> 00:01:27.480
Could it be
there is a living person inside?

00:01:27.680 --> 00:01:28.840
You are mistaken, Young Lady.

00:01:28.840 --> 00:01:29.560
Do you think

00:01:29.560 --> 00:01:31.040
the dead can rise again?

00:01:31.120 --> 00:01:31.879
Step aside quickly.

00:01:32.200 --> 00:01:34.490
Do not let this interfere
with your wedding's good fortune.

00:01:37.959 --> 00:01:38.519
You...

00:01:58.719 --> 00:02:00.159
Thank you for saving me, Young Lady.

00:02:00.850 --> 00:02:02.560
I will surely repay
your kindness one day.

00:02:02.600 --> 00:02:04.990
The coffin bearers confessed
they were acting on someone's orders.

00:02:05.439 --> 00:02:06.599
Do you not want to pursue

00:02:07.000 --> 00:02:08.520
the person who tried to bury you alive?

00:02:10.840 --> 00:02:12.360
I am just a weak woman,

00:02:13.280 --> 00:02:14.319
with a wretched life.

00:02:15.039 --> 00:02:16.400
I will accept my fate.

00:02:17.599 --> 00:02:18.560
Accept your fate?

00:02:19.237 --> 00:02:20.517
He wounded one of your eyes,

00:02:20.800 --> 00:02:22.159
you should blind both of his.

00:02:22.919 --> 00:02:24.199
He trapped you in a coffin,

00:02:24.560 --> 00:02:26.280
you should bury him underground instead!

00:02:30.560 --> 00:02:31.560
Young Lady Shen,

00:02:31.759 --> 00:02:33.120
you are capable of that,

00:02:33.680 --> 00:02:34.800
but I am not.

00:02:35.320 --> 00:02:37.980
Life and death, good fortune and ill
are all destined by Heaven.

00:02:46.319 --> 00:02:46.919
Xi Yan,

00:02:50.039 --> 00:02:51.080
you must live well.

00:02:51.479 --> 00:02:52.639
If someone wishes you dead,

00:02:52.919 --> 00:02:54.479
you must strive even harder to live.

00:02:54.780 --> 00:02:56.919
Who says life and death
are determined by providence?

00:02:57.360 --> 00:03:00.400
We shall defy heaven
and seize our own fate.

00:03:11.280 --> 00:03:13.120
(I rescued Xi Yan by chance that day.)

00:03:13.639 --> 00:03:15.280
(From then on, the destinies of us)

00:03:15.280 --> 00:03:16.500
(became closely intertwined.)

00:03:17.360 --> 00:03:19.880
(Since Pei Yu has already
become suspicious of my identity,)

00:03:20.120 --> 00:03:21.759
(I shall stage a performance for him.)

00:04:02.162 --> 00:04:04.050
=The Architect=

00:04:04.225 --> 00:04:05.150
=Episode 6=
(The more she explains)

00:04:05.150 --> 00:04:06.150
=Episode 6=
