00:04:12.719 --> 00:04:15.000
Shen Changning.

00:04:16.279 --> 00:04:18.240
I have fulfilled your request,

00:04:18.759 --> 00:04:21.199
and found your maid, Lian.

00:04:22.120 --> 00:04:26.000
Do not trouble my dreams anymore.

00:04:28.420 --> 00:04:30.879
What is your connection
to the Shen family's eldest daughter?

00:04:42.560 --> 00:04:43.279
She...

00:04:45.120 --> 00:04:47.639
She is my life-saver.

00:04:48.519 --> 00:04:49.639
If it were not for her,

00:04:49.920 --> 00:04:52.439
I would have already become a corpse.

00:04:54.319 --> 00:04:56.120
So, since she died,

00:04:56.639 --> 00:04:59.199
I must live on for her.

00:04:59.399 --> 00:05:01.720
As long as there is still someone
from the Shen family,

00:05:02.079 --> 00:05:04.040
I must find them for her.

00:05:07.700 --> 00:05:09.790
When did the Shen family's
eldest daughter save you?

00:05:15.199 --> 00:05:16.120
Drink.

00:05:17.512 --> 00:05:18.992
If you drink, I will tell you.

00:05:22.000 --> 00:05:23.160
Drink...

00:05:32.620 --> 00:05:34.990
Could Xi Yan truly have
a past connection with Young Lady Shen?

00:05:36.560 --> 00:05:38.279
She could have said this at any time,

00:05:39.040 --> 00:05:41.220
yet she chose to say it precisely
when I suspected her.

00:05:41.650 --> 00:05:43.780
The more she explains,
the more suspicious she becomes.

00:05:43.862 --> 00:05:45.063
She protests too much.

00:05:48.639 --> 00:05:50.199
But the coroner has already confirmed

00:05:50.519 --> 00:05:52.360
that Young Lady Shen is indeed deceased.

00:05:52.680 --> 00:05:54.120
It seems this Xi Yan

00:05:54.800 --> 00:05:56.720
is deeply involved with the Shen family.

00:06:00.759 --> 00:06:01.399
Young Lady.

00:06:01.399 --> 00:06:02.519
Pei Yu has left.

00:06:02.600 --> 00:06:03.862
I checked carefully,

00:06:03.862 --> 00:06:04.959
there are no spies around.

00:06:12.160 --> 00:06:13.680
I wonder if my words just now

00:06:13.680 --> 00:06:14.879
managed to fool him.

00:06:15.920 --> 00:06:17.759
I saw him escort you back to your room,

00:06:18.040 --> 00:06:19.600
but there was no expression on his face.

00:06:20.560 --> 00:06:22.240
I cannot tell.

00:06:26.399 --> 00:06:26.959
Young Lady,

00:06:27.279 --> 00:06:28.360
if I did not fool him,

00:06:28.560 --> 00:06:29.399
what shall we do?

00:06:56.400 --> 00:06:57.639
I am Shen Changning.

00:06:57.839 --> 00:06:58.680
I am not dead.

00:06:59.519 --> 00:07:01.279
So, since she died,

00:07:01.800 --> 00:07:04.160
I must live on for her.

00:07:04.360 --> 00:07:06.600
As long as there is still someone
from the Shen family,

00:07:06.759 --> 00:07:08.720
I must find them for her.

00:07:53.560 --> 00:07:55.360
I shall assist Your Lordship
with his bath.

00:08:17.319 --> 00:08:18.480
What is the meaning of this?

00:08:28.570 --> 00:08:30.600
When Xiao Huaijin previously
entered the Residence,

00:08:30.920 --> 00:08:32.000
he threatened me,

00:08:32.120 --> 00:08:33.590
wanting me to assassinate the Governor.

00:08:38.279 --> 00:08:39.080
If that is the case,

00:08:39.919 --> 00:08:41.279
why did you not comply?

00:08:42.879 --> 00:08:44.360
I naturally knows

00:08:44.679 --> 00:08:46.799
who the truly reliable person is.

00:08:59.440 --> 00:09:01.879
Other than this dagger you carry,

00:09:03.279 --> 00:09:04.960
do you have any other weapons?

00:09:14.360 --> 00:09:15.279
Are you intending

00:09:15.759 --> 00:09:16.840
to switch your allegiance,

00:09:17.360 --> 00:09:18.320
and work for me?

00:09:18.450 --> 00:09:24.337
♪Loneliness, how do I cross it?
Whom have I ever failed?♪

00:09:24.737 --> 00:09:25.975
♪Incense burns through a few sticks♪

00:09:26.039 --> 00:09:28.279
I know Your Lordship
is a man of noble character,

00:09:28.679 --> 00:09:30.000
and great righteousness.

00:09:30.060 --> 00:09:32.399
You are also political rivals
with Prince Duan's Residence.

00:09:34.020 --> 00:09:37.380
♪Unwilling to forgive past mistakes♪

00:09:37.900 --> 00:09:43.140
♪Blaming myself for not protecting
our vows as I should have♪

00:09:44.660 --> 00:09:47.660
